        "Title": "The wine heist",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN",
        "PublicId": "103187442704",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository e3db9074-6b09-4105-8953-4884d88bc039).Image",
        "Description": "After several weeks at see, 47 ran out of wine.\rEvery buccaneer knows there is only one way to get new wine.\rAnd this way contains robbery, murder and a lot of style. \r\r47 has a simple plan:\r1. Raid the Caruso villa \r2. Kill the head of the wine cellar\r3. Plunder the wine \r4. Drink the wine within the next week.\r\rBut on his way back he was distracted by those landlubbers with their fishing roads and plants. So he quickly got rid of them and escaped with his boat.  \r\rGood luck hearties.",
